metadata.name: Furucombo x Aave (Special)
metadata.description:
Limited-special-edition NFT - Collaboration between Furucombo, Aave, and Lootex
Special Level - Aave cube Zone
A cute Aave Ghost sends you a love message telling you that it can't wait to meet you at Furucombo's Aave cube! *Tip for entering the Special Level: You must meet all the Aave Ghosts in the Furucombo maze!
